  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d51a464d285dc602bdc290",
      "text": "関西学院大学",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573931,
      "updated": 1775573931
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51ba8000000000011263d",
      "text": "くゎんせいがくゐんだいがく",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573931,
      "updated": 1775573931
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bab000000000011263f",
      "text": "Kwansei Gakuin University",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573931,
      "updated": 1775573932
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bac0000000000112640",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573932,
      "updated": 1775573932
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bac0000000000112641",
      "text": "日本の私立大学の名称",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573933,
      "updated": 1775573937
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bb10000000000112642",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573937,
      "updated": 1775573937
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bb10000000000112643",
      "text": "> 1886年（明治19年）8月に来日した米国南メソヂスト監督教会宣教師J.W.ランバス一家は、同年11月に神戸・元町の外国人居留地に読書館を設立し、後に多額の資金援助と大量の書籍を提供した米国・ミズーリ州の牧師W.B.パルモアにちなんで読書館をパルモア学院と命名した。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573938,
      "updated": 1775573952
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bbf0000000000112644",
      "text": "> 1889年（明治22年）9月28日、J.W.ランバスの長男[W.R.ランバス]によって、いわゆる「[原田の森]」（[兵庫県]菟原郡原田村、現在の[神戸市]灘区王子町・原田通）に関西学院（英文表記: Kwansei Gakuin`[注釈 1]`/West Japan College）が創立された。当初は、神学部および普通学部の2学部から始まった。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573952,
      "updated": 1775574109
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bc40000000000112645",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/関西学院大学 via.]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573957,
      "updated": 1775573966
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51baa000000000011263e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573931,
      "updated": 1775573931
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51be10000000000112646",
      "text": "スクール・モットー",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573985,
      "updated": 1775573990
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bee0000000000112648",
      "text": " Mastery for Service",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573999,
      "updated": 1775574003
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bf20000000000112649",
      "text": " 奉仕のための練達",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574003,
      "updated": 1775574006
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51be30000000000112647",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775573990,
      "updated": 1775573990
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bf6000000000011264a",
      "text": "エンブレム",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574007,
      "updated": 1775574010
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bf9000000000011264c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/2503ca149b08086b0bc763969098b31e]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574010,
      "updated": 1775574026
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c09000000000011264d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574026,
      "updated": 1775574026
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c0b000000000011264e",
      "text": "校章",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574027,
      "updated": 1775574032
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c10000000000011264f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1ee005cba713e941e85dc1c26d33e3ee]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574033,
      "updated": 1775574043
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c1a0000000000112650",
      "text": "\t覚え方: バナナ キログラム",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574043,
      "updated": 1775574054
    },
    {
      "id": "69d5e911000000000095e000",
      "text": "\t意味が2つある",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775626514,
      "updated": 1775626516
    },
    {
      "id": "69d5e903000000000095dfff",
      "text": " \t今は未熟だが三日月が徐々に満月になるように少しずつ成長していこう",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775626500,
      "updated": 1775626517
    },
    {
      "id": "69d5e916000000000095e001",
      "text": " \t月が自ら光らないことと同様に、我々も神の光を地上に照らし返すような存在になりましょう",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775626518,
      "updated": 1775626569
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51bf8000000000011264b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574010,
      "updated": 1775574010
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c2d0000000000112654",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574062,
      "updated": 1775574062
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c2a0000000000112651",
      "text": "母校[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574058,
      "updated": 1775574060
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c2c0000000000112653",
      "text": "\t中高大と10年通った",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1775574061,
      "updated": 1775574072
    },
    {
      "id": "69d51c2c0000000000112652",
      "text": "\tお～、なかなか良い学歴[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775574060,
      "updated": 1775602437
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0d0400000000001ec730",
      "text": "\tいえいえ[Summer498.icon]さんほどではないかと[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776094469,
      "updated": 1776094483
    },
    {
